text: Rogério Dezorzi is a boxer from Brazil. Dezorzi competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics. He was born on 12 August 1966.Rogério Dezorzi == References == Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Brazilian boxers Category:Olympians for Brazil Category:Sportspeople from São Paulo
